<p>As for the easier stuff, you’ll find it all under <a href="https://www.altcointrading.net/guides/">Guides</a> in the top menu. Think of it as the basics of the basics: A good example is this <a href="/bitfinex-app/">guide on how to correctly set up your Bitfinex mobile app</a> so that you don’t defeat the purpose of it’s (pretty good) security features just because you’re being careless.</p>

<p>There’s going to be more stuff on how to start trading in this section later on.</p>

